The movie is about the quality of a crappy made for tv movie. There are stupid mock interviews, really shitty head cam shots (why they are in there is a mystery as it adds nothing), and crappy cinematography. The action is just crap as well. 

Unless you are really bored, I suggest a pass on this movie.
